^ http://www.maritime-executive.com/pressrelease/wartsila-joins-global-sustainable-shipping-initiative-taskforce-shape-future-shipping/ Wärtsilä Joins Global Sustainable Shipping Initiative, a Taskforce to Shape the Future of Shipping. Retrieved 23 February 2011.
^ http://www.power-technology.com/contractors/powerplantequip/wartsila/press28.html, Wärtsilä to Deliver 200MWe Power Plant to Pakistan. Retrieved 23 February 2011.
