 upgrade contracts   Ecuador secures US$1.15bn in upstream investment pledges   Técnicas Reunidas' awards fell on Peru re-tender       Grupo Costanera S.p.A.   Baker Hughes, a GE company   Infraestructura Energética Nova S.A.B. de C.V.   Minera Frisco, S.A.B. de C.V.   Gas Energy Latin America       Texas-Tuxpan pipeline   Ojinaga-El Encino Pipeline   Collipulli Wind Farm   Alto Maipo Hydroelectric Project   Kosten Wind Farm                                       

