Welcome to our Investor pages. The objective of the pages is to offer extensive information on Wärtsilä as an investment.
 








Wärtsilä’s Half year financial report 2017 published 20.7.2017 at 8.30 a.m. EEST 
Report, presentation slides and webcast recording  of the event now available.











Discover the new pathways the company is setting forth upon.
Wärtsilä's Annual Report 2016 is now online.
 











AGM was held on Thursday 2 March 2017 in Helsinki
Decisions of the meeting, minutes of the meeting and the President & CEO's presentation slides  now available.










